	 * the passed-in prototype {@code p}.
	 * 
	 * <p>{@code null} will be returned if:
	 * <ul>
	 *   <li>The passed-in method or prototype are {@code null}</li>
	 *   <li>The method does not exist on the prototype chain.</li>
	 * </ul>
